  Stable on ppc.

  02 Jun 2006; Guy Martin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> openexr-1.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on hppa.

  20 May 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/openexr-1.2.2-asneeded.patch, openexr-1.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Add patch to fix building with --as-needed, thanks to Thomas S. Howard in
  bug #133828.

  03 May 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Update metadata to list media-video@gentoo.org as maintainer.

  27 Apr 2006; Marien Zwart <marienz@gentoo.org> files/digest-openexr-1.0.7,
  Manifest:
  Fixing SHA256 digest, pass four

  25 Apr 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  openexr-1.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Don't use /var/tmp for tests temporary data, use $T instead. Thanks to Beech
  Horn in bug #130585 for reporting.

  14 Apr 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  openexr-1.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Add elibtoolize and mark ~x86-fbsd.

*openexr-1.2.2-r2 (18 Dec 2005)

